Pre-Game Insights: Algeria has not lost an AFCON qualifying match on home soil since 2007.
Algeria's recent form across all competitions highlights a strong side, currently enjoying a three-match winning streak.
Others: The hosts will be confident of building on their recent form under their new manager.

Togo enter this game with a sense of urgency, having drawn both of their opening group games and will need to secure points to distance themselves from the other two teams in the group to maintain their qualification hopes.
